overview.en: ArtemisFinance is dedicated to building the next generation of decentralized financial platforms that provide better liquidity and collapse compatibility for crypto assets. Allowing users to conduct P2C (Peer-to- Contract), Artemis empowers financial derivatives and crypto assets with a one-stop solution that provides all the support needed for the DeFi ecosystem.
overview.zh: Artemis 致力于建设下一代分布式的金融平台，为加密资产提供更好的流动性和垮链兼容性。Artemis 允许用户进行P2C（对等合约），通过对分布式金融业务流程的抽象和封装，用一站式解决方案赋能金融衍生品与加密资产，为Defi应用生态提供一切需要的底层支持。
